<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <%-include('base/header.ejs') %>

        <title>Register</title>
</head>

<body>
    <%-include('base/navbarTop.ejs')-%>
        <div class="reg-div">
            <div class="container w-25 border py-3" style="width: 120px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)">
                <div class="title bp-5">
                    <h2 class="font-weight-bold text-center">Sign Up</h2>
                    <small class="text-muted text-center">계정을 생성하려면 아래 공백란을 모두 입력해주세요.</small>

                    <form action="/auth/register_process" method="post"><br>
                        <input type="text" placeholder="ID" class="form-control" name="userId" id="userId" required><br>
                        <input type="email" placeholder="이메일 주소" class="form-control" name="email" id="email" required><br>
                        <input type="text" placeholder="이름" class="form-control" name="uname" id="uname" required><br>
                        <input type="number" placeholder="나이 입력" class="form-control form-control-sm" name="age" id="age" required><br>
                        <input type="password" placeholder="비밀번호" class="form-control" name="psw" id="psw" required>
                        <small class="text-muted text-left text-sm">영문, 숫자, 특수문자 포함 8자리 이상</small>
                        <input type="password" placeholder="비밀번호 다시입력" class="form-control" name="pswr" id="pswr" required><br>

                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" onclick="location.href='/'">취소</button>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-success">회원가입</button><br>

                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <%-include('base/footer.ejs')%>
</body>

</html>